Direct Known Subclasses:
AddNewEntryStrategy, AddNewTableStrategy, CreateNewOrderStrategy, PrintNewBillStrategy, RemoveEntryStrategy, RemoveOrderStrategy, RemoveTableStrategy, SetOrderToDeliveredStrategy, SetOrderToNotPreparableStrategy, SetOrderToPreparedStrategy, SetOrderToSeenStrategy
public abstract class StrategyAbstract extends Object implements StrategyInterface
Strategy abstract class. Each strategy has a execute method in common, this is the gateway to every other method you put in your strategy, since it's the only method that is invoked by the controller.
